      "value": "<p>In your most dire moments, you summon a primal desire to survive that pushes you beyond your limits.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Con 17</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Once per day, when you spend Resolve Points to stay in the fight, you regain Hit Points equal to 1 + your Constitution modifier ([[/ max(0, floor(@abilities.con.mod + 1))]]), and you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to skill checks, attack rolls, and saving throws for a number of rounds equal to the Hit Points regained in this way.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.effects.Item.uyLbbMv6J65o9Ngu]{Effect: Grim Determination (Combat)}</p>"
